title: Funk You Natural Food
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Western, Juice bar, Bakery, German
description: Little health food restaurant with a juice bar inside Inside Bikini Berlin since 2015; previously at Gartnerstrasse 21. Makes raw food, smoothies, and vegan range including cakes, sandwiches, soups, and vegan breakfast items. Some gluten free. Free Wi-Fi.
